      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "June 2, 1950",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover, director",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Pennsylvania Avenue at 9th, NW",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Washington, D.C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "I am currently engaged in research for a graduate",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "dissertation which will attempt to analyze the socio-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "logical and psychological implications of the flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "saucer phenomenon.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "In the course of my research I am giving extensive",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "consideration of the several magazine articles and the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "one book which have already been written on the subject.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "The book, in particular, and the magazine articles in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "general, hint at official restraints which have hampered",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "the authors in their research. So far as I know none of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "those research projects attempted to probe as deeply into",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "the background of the phenomena as I am, yet I have en-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "countered no such \"official censorship\" as they mention.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "In fact I have been surprised at the openness with which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "some people have replied to my queries.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "I believe the fact that I have encountered no restric-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "tions is significant when I attempt to analyze my total",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "findings. It raises the question as to whether those",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "previously mentioned authors aren't trying hard to sell",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "something which really isn't there to sell.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Is there any reason why the flying saucer situation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "should be \"played down?\" Is there any official attitude",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "toward the matter?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "I wish to thank you in advance for your interest and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "help. You may be assured that I will appreciate any infor-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "mation you may be able to give me.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
